<br>
What do people consider an optimal AC?<br>
<br>
Up till now, I've just been concentrating on pumping AC.  I was in the mid 900s for the longest time.  Buffed, I'd pop up to the low 1000's.  But recently I was able to upgrade several of my worst pieces of armor (eg, traded out a golden black pearl choker (+7 dex/agil, but no AC) for a glimmering mithril torque (AC 15, Str 2)).  As a result, my AC shot up quickly.  Self-buffed I'm at 1031 now.<br>
